03:34.800 --> 03:35.872
Give me your hand.

03:37.479 --> 03:38.496
Give me your hand.

03:46.840 --> 03:47.840
you...

03:54.680 --> 03:56.000
When we were in Shangzhou,

03:57.400 --> 03:59.120
One night,
a bag of chestnuts was given.

04:00.120 --> 04:02.360
Did you peel it off?

04:07.879 --> 04:08.896
Rong Yu,

04:10.919 --> 04:12.319
You are indeed a good person.

04:13.759 --> 04:15.800
