04:16.680 --> 04:17.800
but i did it

04:17.800 --> 04:19.040
So much to embarrass him.

04:21.879 --> 04:23.040
today,

04:25.240 --> 04:27.160
I sincerely want to ask

04:29.360 --> 04:30.464
sorry.

