Contrary to what Miss He thought,

05:44.000 --> 05:45.959
He and I find astrology
interesting.

05:47.360 --> 05:48.400
everyone's destiny

05:48.400 --> 05:49.800
Written on the vast starry sky.

05:51.040 --> 05:52.288
