06:08.720 --> 06:09.792
like what?

06:10.319 --> 06:11.392
like what?

06:15.959 --> 06:17.140
I will tell

06:17.140 --> 06:18.199
The story of the late emperor.

06:19.519 --> 06:21.079
The life of the late emperor?

06:22.680 --> 06:24.160
