07:13.600 --> 07:15.900
Won't you tell
the story of the late emperor?

07:15.900 --> 07:17.088
Come.

07:20.120 --> 07:22.319
Thanks to the predictions of astrology,

07:22.319 --> 07:24.880
The emperor married
a woman he did not love.

07:24.880 --> 07:26.179
Still the person he truly loved

07:26.179 --> 07:28.320
Because of him, he became Jia Lin’s hostage.

07:28.320 --> 07:29.580
hope she can

07:29.580 --> 07:30.880
Stay with the late emperor.

07:30.880 --> 07:32.439
After going through many difficulties,

07:33.279 --> 07:34.899
at the end,

07:34.899 --> 07:36.120
