09:01.240 --> 09:02.368
Do you want me to drink?

09:04.720 --> 09:05.824
he's good.

09:12.600 --> 09:15.099
Wait a moment.

09:15.099 --> 09:17.440
I...
I still have something to say.

09:19.000 --> 09:20.159
Rong Yu.

09:20.159 --> 09:23.300
I just
apologized to you,

