Take Ling for a walk.

25:59.119 --> 26:00.140
Better than staying

26:00.140 --> 26:01.279
Trapped at home.

26:04.440 --> 26:05.799
Okay, looks great.

26:07.799 --> 26:09.119
But we must remember her

26:11.079 --> 26:12.480
Not to mention Rong Yu

26:13.200 --> 26:14.240
In front of Ling.

26:14.960 --> 26:16.000
Sim.

26:22.880 --> 26:23.936
What's wrong?

26:24.440 --> 26:26.759
——Why did the young master faint?
- I have no idea.

26:32.440 --> 26:34.640
what happened?

26:34.640 --> 26:36.079
Why?

26:39.200 --> 26:41.000
Are there any signs that he's going to wake up?

26:41.680 --> 26:43.020
winter is very cold.

26:43.020 --> 26:44.559
The cold air was trapped in his body,

26:45.200 --> 26:47.119
His pulse weakened again.

26:47.839 --> 26:49.639
Until we find a solution,

26:49.639 --> 26:52.840
I suggest taking the young master to the manor

26:52.840 --> 26:54.240
With thermal water and geothermal heat.

26:54.240 --> 26:56.199
Taking a hot spring bath every day
can help improve your physical condition.

26:56.199 --> 26:58.000
